I look at the mirror and can't believe what I see! I see a very charming and beautiful woman inI say "I wish to be rich."

I say "I will have you removed from my shoulder and placed in a nice jar." The bee says "Your Majesty, I will do that but I must tell you that I am not a bee, I am a tiny fairy." I say "A fairy?" "Yes, I am a fairy and I will grant you three wishes." I say "I wish to be the most beautiful woman in the world." The fairy says "Your wish is granted." I look at the mirror and can't believe what I see! I see a very charming and beautiful woman in the mirror. "Is it me?" I askI say "I wish to be rich."

I say "I will have you removed from my shoulder and placed in a nice jar." The bee says "Your Majesty, I will do that but I must tell you that I am not a bee, I am a tiny fairy." I say "A fairy?" "Yes, I am a fairy and I will grant you three wishes." I say "I wish to be the most beautiful woman in the world." The fairy says "Your wish is granted." I look at the mirror and can't believe what I see! I see a very charming and beautiful woman in the mirror. "Is it me?" I asked the fairy. The fairy said it is. I say "I wish to be rich." The fairy says "Your wish is granted." I check my bank balance online which shows $10 millions! I am greedy and say "I wish to have a big house." The fairy says "Your wish is granted." A

I say "I will have you removed from my shoulder and placed in a nice jar." The bee says "Your Majesty, I will do that but I must tell you that I am not a bee, I am a tiny fairy." I say "A fairy?" "Yes, I am a fairy and I will grant you three wishes." I say "I wish to be the most beautiful woman in the world." The fairy says "Your wish is granted." I look at the mirror and can't believe what I see! I see a very charming and beautiful woman in the mirror. "Is it me?" I asked the fairy. The fairy said it is. I say "I wish to be rich." The fairy says "Your wish is granted." I check my bank balance online which shows $10 millions! I am greedy and say "I wish to have a big house." The fairy says "Your wish is granted." A very big and luxurious house appears in front of me and a key lands on my hand! Suddenly I feel stinked. I look at my shoulder and see a bee! A real bee! I scream and the fairy disappears. I'm very sad t
